<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Weird Brains</title>
    <link rel="icon" type="image/x-icon" href="/images/favicon.png">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles.css">
    <link
        href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@500&family=Montserrat:wght@900&family=Poppins:wght@400;600;700&family=Roboto&family=Roboto+Mono:wght@300;400;500&family=Ubuntu:ital@0;1&display=swap"
        rel="stylesheet">
    <script src="https://kit.fontawesome.com/919e7ddcdd.js" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
</head>

<body>
    <section id="hero">
        <h1>Weird Brains</h1>
    </section>

    <section id="description">
        <div>
            <h1>Who We Are?</h1>
            <p>A thriving community that values collaboration and mutual support is a remarkable force that can enable
                individuals to grow and achieve their goals. Here at Weird Brains, members are driven by a common
                interest, passion and purpose, such as technology or innovation, and are committed to helping each other
                in any way possible. Weird Brains is characterized by a range of events and opportunities that promote
                learning and development, such as hackathons, tech-related events, internships, and other programs.
                These events allow members to connect, learn from one another, and push each other to be their best.
                Ultimately, our community creates a dynamic and supportive ecosystem that fosters creativity,
                innovation, and progress.</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="member-body">
        <h1>Our Members</h1>
        <div class="wrapper">
        <% for(var i=0; i < dataSet.length; i++){ %>
                <div class="sub-wrapper">
                    <div class="img-div">
                        <img style="border-radius: 50%;" src=<%=dataSet[i].avatar %> alt="Not found" onerror="this.src='images/discord.png';" >
                    </div>
                    <div class="info-div">
                        <h3>
                            <%= dataSet[i].name %>
                        </h3>
                        <span>
                            <%= dataSet[i].discordUserName %>
                        </span>
                        <ul class="socials-list">
                            <li><a href=<%=dataSet[i].linkedIn %> target="_blank" class="href"><i
                                        class="fa-brands fa-linkedin social-icons"></i></a></li>
                            <li><a href=<%=dataSet[i].github %> target="_blank" class="href"><i
                                        class="fa-brands fa-github social-icons"></i></a></li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            <% } %>
        </div>
    </section>
    <section id="footer">
        <h3>Wish to join? <a href="mailto:contact@kraparesh.co">Get in touch!</a></h3>
        <h4>Â© Weird Brains | 2023</h4>
    </section>
</body>

</html>